# Cursor Rules for TrackVolt Project

## MANDATORY: Read Before Any Work
Before making ANY changes, you MUST read these files:
1. AGENTS.md — Critical safety rules and project context
2. TRACKVOLT_MASTER_DOC.md — Full project documentation

## Key Facts
- LOCAL code ≠ PRODUCTION code. Production has 15+ more features.
- NEVER deploy to production (npx vercel --prod) without user confirmation.
- Safe rollback deployment: GTeJwY1rw
- TypeScript strict mode: unused imports = build failure.
- IndexedDB is per-origin: localhost data ≠ trackvolt.app data (expected).

## Design Tokens
Primary accent: #C8FF00 (volt green)
Background: #0D0D14 → #13131E → #1A1A28 (layered depth)
Text: #F0F0F8 → #8888A0 → #50505E

## When Making Code Changes
1. Edit files
2. Run: npm run build (must pass)
3. Run: npm run dev (test locally)
4. STOP — tell user, do NOT deploy
